001package org.nasdanika.architecture.core.gen;
002
003import java.util.ArrayList;
004import java.util.Collection;
005
006import org.nasdanika.html.model.app.gen.SemanticSiteGenerator;
007import org.nasdanika.html.model.app.gen.SiteGeneratorContributor;
008
009public class CoreSiteGenerator extends SemanticSiteGenerator {
010
011        @Override
012        protected Collection<SiteGeneratorContributor> getContributors() {
013                Collection<SiteGeneratorContributor> contributors = new ArrayList<>(super.getContributors());
014                contributors.add(new CoreSiteGeneratorContributor());
015                return contributors;
016        }
017
018}
